  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK609">
<l>kuṭiyāṇmai yuḷvanta kuṟṟa moruvaṉ </l>
<l>maṭiyāṇmai māṟṟak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a man puts away idleness, the reproach which has come upon himself and his family will disappear.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
